Watch the Event Unleash Your Potential Take Yourself to the Next Level Unlock the keys to your limitless potential Attend to Course ABOUT US Welcome Welcome to our DTP Leadership website! We are delighted to have you here as we embark on a collective journey to explore the art of effective leadership. As passionate and experienced leaders, we believe in the transformative power of inspiring others, fostering collaboration, and driving positive change. This platform serves as a gateway into our world of leadership, where we aim to share insights, strategies, and experiences that can empower individuals and organizations to reach their full potential. Join us as we delve into the realm of leadership philosophy, practical tips, and thought-provoking discussions. Together, let’s unlock the key to exceptional leadership and make a lasting impact in the world. Read More About Us OUR PROGRAMS What You Will Learn From Us Emotional Connection Our foundational program guides you in identifying emotional triggers, processing feelings, and making informed decisions. Led by our experienced team, DTP offers systematic practice and creative exercises, empowering you to enhance your emotional quotient. Learn more on how to create a journey towards stronger relationships and profound self-discovery! Learn More About this → Habitual Patterns Explore your habits with DTP's unique assessment, pinpointing 17 key patterns. Tired of fleeting changes? Our assessment provides personalized insights, empowering lasting transformations in your behavior and interactions. Dive into profound emotional experiences and effective leadership! Learn More About this → Leadership Embrace the transformative power of our leadership program, where genuine leadership begins: within yourself. Explore your leadership potential with the Leadership Practices Inventory® (LPI) and our Habitual Patterns Assessment. Start your journey to authentic leadership today! Learn More About this → Building Relationships Through Appreciating Differences Join DTP Leadership Group’s transformative journey in Building Relationships Through Appreciating Differences. With 50 years of expertise, we empower organizations with transformative programs focused on leveraging different perspectives. Our assessments and emotional connection training break barriers. Let us guide your organization to thrive and build relationships through appreciating differences. Experience the future of work with DTP Leadership! Learn More About this → Executive Coaching Ready to break barriers and reach new heights? DTP's Executive Coaching is your ticket to personal and professional growth. Our experienced coaches, Dr. Jackalyn Rainosek and Liz Cloud, empower you to overcome challenges, enhance skills, and achieve your goals. Discover a confidential space for transformation. Your journey to success starts here. Dive in today! Learn More About this → Visionary Dream Coaching Embark on a transformative journey with DTP's Visionary Dream Coaching. Discover your purpose, overcome barriers, and manifest your dreams. Our certified coaches offer personalized sessions, exercises, and journaling, creating a safe space for your growth. Embrace a richer, more meaningful life. Start your visionary journey now! Learn More About this → DTP Business Strategies Elevate your business with DTP Business Strategies! Led by Dr. Jackalyn Rainosek, our team offers tailored solutions for revenue and profit growth. Unlock your business's potential and dominate your market. Ready to thrive and secure your success? Learn More About this → Organizational Development Consulting Transform your organization with DTP Leadership Group. We guide you through change, refining purpose, vision, and interactions for success in today's dynamic world. Our experts enhance leadership skills, foster clear communication, and build equitable workplaces. Experience improved productivity and collaboration. Elevate your business today! Learn More About this → EXPERIENCED MENTORS Meet Our Team Dr. Jackalyn Rainosek Captain Allan Post Sahira J. Abdool, MPA, MHA, MHR Jowell Lydon Linda Snook Robert C. Hernandez Lori Walters Liz Cloud Meet DTP Leadership Group, LLC TESTIMONIALS What Our Clients Say About Us “I owe so much to Dr Jackalyn she’s helped give me confidence she helped me navigate through the transition from middle management to Executive leadership.” Lori Walters “Your program has really helped me hone and develop where I need to be, where I need to go, and how to go there.” Bob Hernandez “I love that this is a very systematic way to get clear on your core beliefs, vision, and values so that you can create 10 specific dreams you know like a personal dream, professional dream, Finance dream, family dream, and more.” Joanna Clark “I know where i want to go, I know how to to get there and I know I am making progress.
